text: Pyrausta genialis is a moth in the family Crambidae. It was described by South in 1901. It is found in China. ==Subspecies== *Pyrausta genialis genialis *Pyrausta genialis reductalis Caradja in Caradja & Meyrick, 1937 (China: Yunnan) ==References== Category:Moths described in 1901 generosa Category:Moths of China
title: Pyrausta genialis
